 <title xml:id="SysMgmtServices">Disable Rdisc</title>
 <para>
  The rdisc daemon is used with the ICMP Router Discovery Protocol
  (IRDP) to assist with network discovery and setup. Since most systems
  typically use static address, or DHCP, it is recommended that the
  service be disabled.
 </para>
